sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant HW as Hardware (Oscillator)
    participant PIT as PIT (8254)
    participant PIC as PIC (8259)
    participant CPU as CPU
    participant OS_Timer as OS (timer.c)
    participant OS_Sched as OS (scheduler)

    Note over OS_Timer: volatile uint32_t tick = 0&#59;

    Note over HW,OS_Sched: Phase 1&#58; Initialization (init_timer)
    Note over CPU, OS_Timer: Kernel Boot calls init_timer(100)
    CPU->>OS_Timer: init_timer(frequency=100)
    activate OS_Timer
    OS_Timer->>OS_Timer: Calculate divisor = 1193180 / 100
    OS_Timer->>PIT: outb(0x43, 0x36) (Set Mode 3)
    OS_Timer->>PIT: outb(0x40, low_byte)
    OS_Timer->>PIT: outb(0x40, high_byte)
    deactivate OS_Timer
    Note over PIT: PIT begins counting down divisor

    Note over HW,OS_Sched: Phase 2&#58; The Tick Loop (Cyclical)
    loop Every ~10ms (100Hz)
        HW->>PIT: Crystal Pulse (1.19318 MHz)
        PIT->>PIT: Decrement Internal Counter
        alt Counter reaches 0
            PIT->>PIC: Raise IRQ0 (Interrupt Request)
            activate PIC
            Note right of PIC: PIC latches IRQ0, waits for CPU
            PIC->>CPU: INTR (Interrupt Signal)
            activate CPU
            Note right of CPU: CPU finishes current instruction
            CPU->>PIC: Interrupt Acknowledge (INTA)
            PIC->>CPU: Deliver Interrupt Vector (e.g., 0x20)
            deactivate PIC

            Note over CPU: Context Switch to ISR
            CPU->>OS_Timer: Call timer_handler()
            activate OS_Timer

            rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
                Note right of OS_Timer: [timer.c logic]
                OS_Timer->>OS_Timer: tick++ (Advance OS Time)
                OS_Timer->>OS_Timer: Perform CPU Accounting (current_task->ticks++)
                OS_Timer->>OS_Timer: Call gui_handle_timer()
            end

            OS_Timer->>PIC: outb(0x20, 0x20) (Send EOI)
            Note right of PIC: PIC can now accept new interrupts

            OS_Timer->>OS_Sched: Call schedule() (Preemptive Multitasking)
            activate OS_Sched
            Note over OS_Sched: Context Switch to Next Task
            deactivate OS_Sched

            deactivate OS_Timer
            deactivate CPU
        end
        Note over PIT: Wait for next Pulse (if counter > 0)
    end
